話？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n學校需要？  因為同學唔識廣東話？  自己唔識廣東話？？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢地講得超流利"},{"pid":"844f94981f1f3594ce86fbba8e02f1964f4aa8e0","tid":468440,"uid":40445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T11:37:12.000Z","msg":"係呀<br />\n過多十年，廿年，佢地結婚生仔，用普通話母語教細路<br />\n廣東語母語比例會顯著下趺架啦"},{"pid":"29141973772c228fa5d7b1a42772dfd8b8b07052","tid":468440,"uid":85564,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T11:59:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實著住校服果班因咩事會講普通話？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n學校需要？  因為同學唔識廣東話？  自己唔識廣東話？？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢地講得超流利</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n大陸人黎咖，佢地係全級大陸人咁收生，全級都係"},{"pid":"7b8b4c0f2358b84635b8363f3418e7afc00e1d75","tid":468440,"uid":154750,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T12:04:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>其實著住校服果班因咩事會講普通話？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n學校需要？  因為同學唔識廣東話？  自己唔識廣東話？？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢地講得超流利</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n大陸人黎咖，佢地係全級大陸人咁收生，全級都係</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔係呱！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我剩係識過一個中學生，同佢傾電話時聽到佢同人講普通話，我問佢點解要講，佢話同班同佢最fd既都係講普通話，所以要就佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51118533703abfc724e7a38f4640d7604339c783","tid":468440,"uid":52591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T12:08:38.000Z","msg":"二三十年後咪完全比中國同化囉，幾千年都咁work"},{"pid":"894df9732c4de1f345f45b6c7a11ae5d07962bef","tid":468440,"uid":14190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T12:10:32.000Z","msg":"陰道式滅族"},{"pid":"1acbb4ff94566efa280d1a29585abde267c26f7e","tid":468440,"uid":54929,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T12:35:15.000Z","msg":"今日我喺見到咁樣樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我知有啲學校淨喺收蝗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"079da470a6d666df6db982dfe0d574397934effa","tid":468440,"uid":54929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T12:35:38.000Z","msg":"啲學生就喺咁慢慢同化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74705c47bd56a9f26826c425345991a823aae259","tid":468440,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T12:36:14.000Z","msg":"上次去上水<br />\n<br />\n公屋<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n全家都講，老豆都講北方普通話"},{"pid":"32010e5b4d1bf9c35c0fd675a873c49b2268e3a1","tid":468440,"uid":18241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T12:37:27.000Z","msg":"香港市指日可待"},{"pid":"dc4188443d9b44090bdba3615fab06f41971c226","tid":468440,"uid":21595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T12:38:12.000Z","msg":"日日都俾人換緊血 玩撚完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b15315c3e532313cd6ed3ad0b8f575446d240ed","tid":468440,"uid":9286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T12:41:04.000Z","msg":"而家小學就教緊寫殘體字 痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n以前我讀小學規定一定要寫正體字"},{"pid":"b8ad799ca68618cff0af81662e77ed8dbebc4527","tid":468440,"uid":75466,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T12:44:30.000Z","msg":"住港島未聽過"},{"pid":"8dbb72f184bbc24f91ff88d04de576864187736f","tid":468440,"uid":28358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T12:48:38.000Z","msg":"仆街 我係街成日都聽到中學生講普通話 仲要係北佬腔 ，但見親都係男學生講 冇女學生講？ 咁即係代表咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aec9829a43e4af1